---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Developer Blog | Ferni
description: Technical insights, API updates, and engineering deep dives from the Ferni Developer Platform team.
permalink: /developers/blog/
---

<style>
  :root {
    --dev-bg: #1a1f16;
    --dev-surface: #252b1f;
    --dev-border: #3d4535;
    --dev-accent: #4a6741;
    --dev-accent-hover: #5a7a4f;
    --dev-accent-light: rgba(74, 103, 65, 0.15);
    --dev-text: #f0ebe4;
    --dev-text-muted: #a8a193;
    --dev-code-bg: #1e2318;
  }

  body {
    background: var(--dev-bg);
    color: var(--dev-text);
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
  }

  .dev-blog-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dev-surface) 0%, var(--dev-bg) 100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--dev-border);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .dev-blog-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    color: var(--dev-text);
  }

  .dev-blog-header p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--dev-text-muted);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .dev-nav {
    background: var(--dev-surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--dev-border);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }

  .dev-nav-brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--dev-text);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .dev-nav-brand svg {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
  }

  .dev-nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .dev-nav-links a {
    color: var(--dev-text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .dev-nav-links a:hover,
  .dev-nav-links a.active {
    color: var(--dev-accent);
  }

  .dev-blog-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .posts-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .post-card {
    background: var(--dev-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--dev-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .post-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--dev-accent);
  }

  .post-card a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .post-card-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--dev-text-muted);
  }

  .post-card-category {
    background: var(--dev-accent-light);
    color: var(--dev-accent);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .post-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--dev-text);
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  .post-card p {
    color: var(--dev-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .post-card-footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--dev-border);
  }

  .post-card-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .post-card-author-avatar {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--dev-accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .post-card-author-name {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .post-card-read-time {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--dev-text-muted);
  }

  .empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    color: var(--dev-text-muted);
  }

  .empty-state h2 {
    color: var(--dev-text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  .dev-footer {
    background: var(--dev-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--dev-border);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--dev-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .dev-footer a {
    color: var(--dev-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .dev-footer a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .dev-blog-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .dev-nav {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .dev-nav-links {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .post-card a {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .post-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<nav class="dev-nav">
  <a href="/developers/" class="dev-nav-brand">
    {# Ferni Avatar: LUXO-style opaque white eyes, NO pupils #}
    <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" fill="#4a6741"/>
      {# Opaque white eyes - NO pupils per brand guidelines #}
      <ellipse cx="35" cy="45" rx="8" ry="10" fill="#FFFDFB"/>
      <ellipse cx="65" cy="45" rx="8" ry="10" fill="#FFFDFB"/>
    </svg>
    <span>Ferni Developers</span>
  </a>
  <ul class="dev-nav-links">
    <li><a href="/developers/">Docs</a></li>
    <li><a href="/developers/api/">API Reference</a></li>
    <li><a href="/developers/blog/" class="active">Blog</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/ferni-ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<header class="dev-blog-header">
  <h1>Developer Blog</h1>
  <p>Technical insights, API updates, and engineering deep dives from the Ferni Developer Platform team.</p>
</header>

<main class="dev-blog-content">
  {% if collections.devPosts.length > 0 %}
    <div class="posts-grid">
      {% for post in collections.devPosts %}
        <article class="post-card">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            <div class="post-card-meta">
              {% if post.data.category %}
                <span class="post-card-category">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
              {% endif %}
              <time datetime="{{ post.date | date('yyyy-MM-dd') }}">
                {{ post.date | date('MMM d, yyyy') }}
              </time>
            </div>
            <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
            {% if post.data.excerpt %}
              <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="post-card-footer">
              <div class="post-card-author">
                <span class="post-card-author-avatar" style="background: {{ post.data.authorColor or '#4a6741' }}">
                  {{ post.data.authorInitials or 'FD' }}
                </span>
                <span class="post-card-author-name">{{ post.data.author or 'Ferni Dev Team' }}</span>
              </div>
              {% if post.data.readTime %}
                <span class="post-card-read-time">{{ post.data.readTime }} min read</span>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <div class="empty-state">
      <h2>Coming Soon</h2>
      <p>We're working on some great content for developers. Check back soon!</p>
    </div>
  {% endif %}
</main>

<footer class="dev-footer">
  <p>&copy; {{ 'now' | date('yyyy') }} Ferni AI. <a href="/developers/">Developer Docs</a> · <a href="/developers/api/">API Reference</a> · <a href="https://ferni.ai">ferni.ai</a></p>
</footer>
